{"tid":469146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機師夢碎兼女友提分手 浸大生稱壓力下摸女童今判感化","createTime":"2017-11-15T04:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T04:52:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2608fe0783bbdaa43fdbbc510078ad714edd7fdd","tid":469146,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T04:52:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171115/large/1510717418_a355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171115%2Flarge%2F1510717418_a355.jpg&h=83e448d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身高約5呎的浸大男生稱因機師夢碎，加上女友提分手，雙重打擊下在8月8日於馬鞍山新港城中心摸10歲女童的臀部。男生早前認罪，父母撰信透露兒子因身高問題常被人取笑，裁判官今指被告的感化報告內容正面，遂依感化官建議判被告接受一年感化，並指希望被告反省後知道做人的方向。<br />\n<br />\n於浸大就讀中國研究學系二年級的被告區梓濠（20歲），回答指明白判刑，裁判官指被告於感化期間須按指示參與小組活動、心理治療及輔導，並問「你做到嗎？」被告回應「做到」。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時指，被告的感化及社會服務令報告正面，他亦獲家人支持，還柙期間有非常大的警醒，不會再犯。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460348&d=wbblXAdUUDw7h6ZmuthJ0E4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=f0f789c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171115%2F57460348&h=5e3fde35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171115/57460348</a>"}]}